<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="he" dir="rtl">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>חינה של נועה ועומר - ניווט</title>
    <style>
        /* פונטים ורקע */
        @import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Suez+One&display=swap');

        body {
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
            background-color: #800000; 
            /* טקסטורה מרוקאית עדינה */
            background-image: url('https://www.transparenttextures.com/patterns/az-subtle.png'); 
            margin: 0;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            align-items: center;
            min-height: 100vh;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 15px;
            box-sizing: border-box;
            color: #fff;
        }

        /* כותרת ראשית */
        h1 {
            color: #f1c40f; 
            font-size: clamp(2rem, 8vw, 3rem);
            margin: 20px 0 5px 0;
            text-shadow: 3px 3px 6px rgba(0,0,0,0.6);
            font-family: 'Suez One', serif;
        }

        .subtitle {
            font-size: 1.1rem;
            margin-bottom: 25px;
            opacity: 0.95;
            letter-spacing: 0.5px;
        }

        /* מיכל הכפתורים */
        .nav-container {
            display: flex;
            gap: 20px;
            width: 100%;
            max-width: 600px;
            flex-direction: column; /* ברירת מחדל למובייל */
            justify-content: center;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }

        /* עיצוב כפתור ניווט */
        .nav-card {
            background: #fff;
            border-radius: 20px;
            box-shadow: 0 10px 25px rgba(0,0,0,0.4);
            padding: 20px;
            text-decoration: none;
            color: #333;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center; /* תצוגת שורה למובייל נוחה יותר */
            border: 3px solid #f1c40f;
            position: relative;
            overflow: hidden;
        }

        .nav-card:active {
            transform: scale(0.98);
        }

        /* אייקון בתוך עיגול */
        .icon-circle {
            width: 60px;
            height: 60px;
            border-radius: 50%;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            font-size: 30px;
            margin-left: 15px;
            flex-shrink: 0;
            border: 2px solid #f1c40f;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 10px rgba(0,0,0,0.2);
        }

        .parking .icon-circle {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #a52a2a 0%, #800000 100%);
        }

        .home .icon-circle {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1abc9c 0%, #16a085 100%);
        }

        .text-content {
            text-align: right;
            flex-grow: 1;
        }

        .card-title {
            font-size: 1.4rem;
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #2c3e50;
            margin: 0;
        }

        .card-desc {
            font-size: 0.9rem;
            color: #7f8c8d;
            margin: 2px 0 0 0;
        }

        /* סקשן טלפונים */
        .phone-section {
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 20px;
            border: 1.5px dashed #f1c40f;
            width: 100%;
            max-width: 600px;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }

        .phone-header {
            color: #f1c40f;
            font-size: 1.4rem;
            font-weight: bold;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            font-family: 'Suez One', serif;
        }

        .phone-grid {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            gap: 15px;
        }

        .phone-link {
            color: #fff;
            text-decoration: none;
            background: rgba(0,0,0,0.5);
            padding: 12px 15px;
            border-radius: 15px;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 8px;
            border: 1px solid #f1c40f;
            transition: all 0.3s;
            flex: 1;
            justify-content: center;
            font-weight: bold;
        }

        .phone-link span {
            font-size: 1.2rem;
        }

        /* עיטורי פינה למובייל */
        .corner {
            position: fixed;
            width: 80px;
            height: 80px;
            opacity: 0.3;
            z-index: -1;
            background-image: url('https://www.transparenttextures.com/patterns/gplay.png');
        }
        .top-right { top: 0; right: 0; }
        .bottom-left { bottom: 0; left: 0; transform: rotate(180deg); }

        /* התאמה למסכים רחבים (טאבלט/מחשב) */
        @media (min-width: 600px) {
            .nav-container {
                flex-direction: row;
            }
            .nav-card {
                flex-direction: column;
                flex: 1;
                padding: 30px;
            }
            .icon-circle {
                margin-left: 0;
                margin-bottom: 15px;
                width: 80px;
                height: 80px;
                font-size: 40px;
            }
            .text-content {
                text-align: center;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <div class="corner top-right"></div>
    <div class="corner bottom-left"></div>

    <h1>קולולולו! <br> נועה ועומר חוגגים חינה 🎉</h1>
    <p class="subtitle">שמחים שאתם באים לחגוג איתנו!</p>

    <div class="nav-container">

        <a href="https://ul.waze.com/ul?place=ChIJX4aHeMCuHRURICdFWKisaPE&ll=32.66259150%2C35.10484200&navigate=yes" class="nav-card parking">
            <div class="icon-circle">🅿️</div>
            <div class="text-content">
                <div class="card-title">לחניה</div>
                <div class="card-desc">חניון סמוך למקום האירוע</div>
            </div>
        </a>

        <a href="https://ul.waze.com/ul?place=ChIJ2fqjE76uHRURypoZ-C-lfZ4&ll=32.66185960%2C35.10944690&navigate=yes" class="nav-card home">
            <div class="icon-circle">🏡</div>
            <div class="text-content">
                <div class="card-title">לבית</div>
                <div class="card-desc">הגעה ישירה למיקום החגיגה</div>
            </div>
        </a>

    </div>
   
    <div class="phone-section">
        <div class="phone-header">לבירורים נוספים:</div>
        <div class="phone-grid">
            <a href="tel:0526039454" class="phone-link">
                <span>📞</span> אהרוני
            </a>
            <a href="tel:0524800922" class="phone-link">
                <span>📞</span> אהובית
            </a>
        </div>
    </div>

</body>
</html>
